title: Group Therapy: She Still Hangs Out With Her Ex
description: Jared called the show today to talk about his now Girlfriend and how she spends a lot of time with her Ex. The only thing we're tripped up on and unsure how we feel is the fact that she does it with her kids who are pretty young.
